						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Developments/CIRAD-INRA-Ethical-guidelines-for-partnerships" title="CIRAD/INRA Ethical guidelines for partnerships" alt="link">CIRAD/INRA Ethical guidelines for partnerships</a></h2>

	
					<p>Partnerships, which are a founding principle for many institutional research centres, are covered by a recent statement by the CIRAD-INRA Joint Consultative Committee on Ethics in Agricultural Research. The statement presents a partnership approach centring on reflexion and debate, and encourages the development of an ethical frame of mind by providing guidelines. It also makes recommendations for the different stakeholders in partnerships. (<a href="http://www.cirad.fr/actualites/toutes-les-actualites/articles/2012/institutionnel/avis-partenariat" target="_blank">CIRAD</a>, 14/06/2012)</p>
							<p><span class="date">11/07/2012</span></p>
